在[[幾何學|幾何學]]中，'''菱形三十面體'''（{{lang|en|Rhombic triacontahedron}}）是一個由[[菱形|菱形]]構成的三十面體<ref>{{Mathworld |urlname=Triacontahedron|title=Triacontahedron}}</ref>，由30個[[全等|全等]]的[[黃金菱形|黃金菱形]]組成，具有60條邊和32個[[頂點_(幾何)|頂點]]，其[[對偶多面體|對偶多面體]]為[[截半二十面体|截半二十面体]]<ref name="RhombicTriacontahedron.Mathworld">{{Mathworld |urlname=RhombicTriacontahedron|title=Rhombic Triacontahedron}}</ref><ref name="Livio Zefiro, DIP.TE.RIS">{{cite web | author=Livio Zefiro, DIP.TE.RIS|url=http://www.mi.sanu.ac.rs/vismath/zefiro/_polyhedra_colouring_2007_08_10.html|title=Review of the alternative choices concerning face colouring of all the regular convex polyhedra and a pair of Catalan polyhedra, the rhombic dodecahedron and the rhombic triacontahedron|publisher=mi.sanu.ac.rs}}</ref>。由於其[[對偶多面體|對偶多面體]]是一個[[半正多面體|半正多面體]]，因此這種立體也屬於[[卡塔蘭多面體|卡塔蘭多面體]]<ref>''The Symmetries of Things'' 2008, John H. Conway, Heidi Burgiel, Chaim Goodman-Strass, ISBN 978-1-56881-220-5 [https://web.archive.org/web/20100919143320/https://akpeters.com/product.asp?ProdCode=2205] (Chapter 21, Naming the Archimedean and Catalan polyhedra and tilings, page 287, pentagonal icosikaitetrahedron)</ref>。

== 性質 ==
菱形三十面體是一個[[卡塔蘭立體|卡塔蘭立體]]<ref name="article can2015metrics">{{Cite journal
  |title=On the metrics induced by icosidodecahedron and rhombic triacontahedron
  |author=Can, Zeynep and Kaya, Rüstem and others
  |journal=KoG
  |volume=19
  |number=19.
  |pages=17-23
  |year=2015
  |publisher=Hrvatsko društvo za geometriju i grafiku}}</ref>，由30個面、60條邊和32個[[頂點_(幾何)|頂點]]組成<ref name="article can2015metrics"/>，其中30面為12個全等的[[黃金菱形|黃金菱形]]，因此是一個[[環帶多面體|環帶多面體]]<ref name="georgehart.com/zonohedra">{{Cite journal | url = http://www.georgehart.com/zonohedra/zonohedrification.html | title = Zonohedrification | author = George W. Hart | journal = The Mathematica Journal | volume = vol. 7 | issue = no. 3 | year = 1999 | access-date = 2018-08-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181114041136/http://www.georgehart.com/zonohedra/zonohedrification.html | archive-date = 2018-11-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，若將菱形三十面體的邊改成與每個面的幾何中心相連接{{#tag:ref|Wenninger (1983)<ref name="Wenninger 1983">{{citation| first=Magnus | last=Wenninger | title=Dual Models | publisher=Cambridge University Press | year=1983 | isbn=0-521-54325-8 | mr = 0730208}}</ref>, "Basic notions about stellation and duality", p. 1.}}，則會形成[[截半二十面体|截半二十面体]]，因此其[[對偶多面體|對偶多面體]]為截半二十面体<ref name="Koca 2010">{{cite journal | author = Koca, Mehmet and Koca, Nazife and Koc, Ramazan
|date = 2010-04
|title = Catalan solids derived from three-dimensional-root systems and quaternions
|volume = 51
|journal = Journal of Mathematical Physics
|doi = 10.1063/1.3356985}}</ref>。

=== 尺寸 ===
若對應的對偶多面體——[[截半二十面體|截半二十面體]]邊長為單位長，則相應的菱形三十面體的[[體積|體積]]為<ref name="RhombicTriacontahedron, dmccooey">{{Cite web | url = http://dmccooey.com/polyhedra/RhombicTriacontahedron.html|title=Catalan Solids: Rhombic Triacontahedron | publisher = dmccooey.com | accessdate = 2020-08-05}}</ref>：
:<math>\frac{25\left(5+2\sqrt{5}\right)}{16} \approx 14.8</math>
而相應幾何體的邊長為<ref name="RhombicTriacontahedron, dmccooey"/>：
:<math>a = \frac{\sqrt{10\left(5+\sqrt{5}\right)}}{8} \approx 1.0633</math>
由此可以推得，如果一个菱形三十面体的棱长为<math>a</math>，那么其体积<math>V</math>與表面积<math>A</math>為<ref name="RhombicTriacontahedron.Mathworld"/>：
:<math>V = 4\sqrt{5+2\sqrt{5}}a^3 \approx 12.3107a^3</math>
:<math>A = 12\sqrt{5}a^2 \approx 26.8328a^2 </math>
中交球半径<math>r_m</math>與內切球半径<math>r_i</math>为<ref name="Stephen Wolfram rhombic triacontahedron">{{Cite WolframAlpha|title=Rhombic triacontahedron|accessdate=7 January 2013}}</ref>：
:<math>r_\mathrm{m}=\left(1+\frac{1}{\sqrt{5}}\right)\,a \approx 1.44721a</math>
:<math>r_\mathrm{i} = \frac{\varphi^2}{\sqrt{1 + \varphi^2}}\,a = \sqrt{1 + \frac{2}{\sqrt{5}}}\,a \approx 1.37638 a</math>
其中''φ''為[[黃金比例|黃金比例]]。

=== 面的組成 ===
{{main|黃金菱形}}
組成菱形三十面體的面皆為全等的[[黃金菱形|黃金菱形]]，其中[[鈍角|鈍角]]的[[角度|角度]]為 116.57°，[[鋭角|鋭角]]的角度則為 63.43°，兩條對角線長度與一邊長的比為<math>\phi:1:\sqrt{\frac{5 + \sqrt{5}}{2}}</math>，長短兩對角線長度的比值為[[黃金比|黃金比]]。<ref name="article can2015metrics"/>
=== 分割 ===
菱形三十面體可以被分割成20個黃金菱形六面體，包括了10個銳角{{link-wd|Q98398187}}和10個鈍角黃金菱形六面體<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.cutoutfoldup.com/979-golden-rhombohedra.php | title = Golden Rhombohedra | author=Laszlo C Bardos | publisher = cutoutfoldup.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/dissection-rt.html | title = Dissection of the rhombic triacontahedron | author = George W. Hart | publisher = Virtual Polyhedra | year = 1996 }}</ref>。
