== 星形化體 ==
{{Main|星形菱形三十面體}}
[[File:Construction_of_Rhombic_hexecontahedron_from_Rhombic_Triacontahedron.gif|thumb]]。]]
菱形三十面體透過全部匹配的星形化方式<ref name="Webb, R. Enumeration">{{Cite web | url = https://www.software3d.com/Enumerate.php | author = Webb, R. | title = "Enumeration of Stellations." | publisher = software3d.com | access-date = 2019-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190427002618/https://www.software3d.com/Enumerate.php | archive-date = 2019-04-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>能夠產生227種星形菱形三十面體<ref>{{cite journal | last = Pawley | first = G. S. | title = The 227 triacontahedra | journal = Geometriae Dedicata | volume = 4 | issue = 2–4 | pages = 221–232 | publisher = Kluwer Academic Publishers | date = 1975 | issn = 1572-9168 | doi = 10.1007/BF00148756}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last = Messer | first = P. W. | title = Stellations of the Rhombic Triacontahedron and Beyond | journal = Structural Topology | volume = 21 | pages = 25–46 | date = 1995}}</ref>。其中[[菱形六十面體|菱形六十面體]]與[[五複合立方體|五複合立方體]]為較具代表性的[[星形菱形三十面體|星形菱形三十面體]]。所有的星形菱形三十面體種類非常繁多，共有358,833,098種星形菱形三十面體，其中包括了84,959個鏡像不變的立體和三億餘種具有手性鏡像的立體<ref name="Webb, R. Enumeration"/>。

其中，[[菱形六十面體|菱形六十面體]]可以透過將菱形三十面體的菱形面沿著長的那一側向外延長稜直到相交來構造<ref name="Kabai, Sándor 2002">{{Cite book | author = Kabai, Sándor | title = "Mathematical Graphics I: Lessons in Computer Graphics Using Mathematica." | location= Püspökladány, Hungary | publisher= Uniconstant | pages= pp. 171, 179, 181 | year= 2002 }}</ref>。
