== 用途 ==
由於菱形三十面體是一種面可遞的立體<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.orchidpalms.com/polyhedra/rhombic/isohedral_rhombihedra.htm | title = Isohedral Rhombohedra | publisher=orchidpalms.com }}</ref>，換句話說，即這立體上的任意兩個面A和B，若透過旋轉或鏡射這個立體，使A移動到B原來的位置時，而兩個面仍然佔據了相同的空間區域<ref>{{citation|title=Dungeons, dragons, and dice|first=K. Robin|last=McLean|journal=The Mathematical Gazette|volume=74|issue=469|year=1990|pages=243–256|jstor=3619822}}.</ref>。由於這種特性使得菱形三十面體有時會成為30面骰子的設計<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.georgehart.com/virtual-polyhedra/dice.html | title = Polyhedral Dice | author = George W. Hart | publisher = Virtual Polyhedra | year = 1996 }}</ref>。

菱形三十面體亦可用於裝飾用途上。丹麥設計師Holger Strøm運用菱形三十面體的結構<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.halodesign.dk/our-designs/iq-light/geometry | title = Halo Design Group, Geometry, IQ light | publisher=halodesign.dk }}</ref>設計了一種可以手工製作的立體燈飾，稱為IQ-light<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.halodesign.dk/our-designs/iq-light/concept | title = The IQlight concept | publisher=halodesign.dk }}</ref>，主要以其獨特的數學結構形成光影美感，用於製造氣氛<ref>{{cite web | url = http://news.library.nptu.edu.tw/files/151-1020-5888.php | title = 創客漾思：IQ Light立體燈DIY | publisher=國立頻東大學圖書館 }}</ref>。亦有藝術家使用菱形三十面體與[[立方體|立方體]]間的幾何關係<ref name="RhombicTriacontahedron.Mathworld"/><ref name="mathworld Cube5-Compound">{{mathworld|urlname=Cube5-Compound |title= Compound of Five Cubes}}</ref>設計出了菱形三十面體造型的收納盒<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://kosticks.com/triacontahedron-box.html | title = triacontahedron box - KO Sticks LLC | publisher = kosticks.com}}</ref>。
